wL29SSc5DhGlqlbyN9Ji2vpxtUiuTKm1mAenUwLq548J-3l87PajrkoY48ABdDuYcuAIx7bjYpDqWSGiJDuiuB6Zp8WRiqihB4pu8-ppGovKZ2RD7ksnBcZ19A6-cz3oPjl6kyyTFMFV_a5ezpX36Gf1ynzHGdAShTQh326-8/Iz1UvmpZ7E0B0dzFF8QfZedM43jyijLd/8" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i3bmWXvyOZVw/v0/-1x-1.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i3bmWXvyOZVw/v0/-1x-1.jpg" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 130%; margin-top: 8px;"&gt;哈佛大学校园的洛厄尔之家。&lt;i&gt;摄影师：梅尔·穆斯托（Mel Musto）/彭博社（Bloomberg）&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;哈佛大学支持特朗普的&lt;/strong&gt;决定激发了民主党领导人的欢呼，但由此产生的联邦&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/TTSlCykQEdNzYqoa1l2TOg5lxA-Qn02jlAtAuSdklnAb6x-K1A-qYuahLWSvPSu0mFjLCqD0U9F7k_GfAVykMeLoy_NC_WSg3sfaklKz7EWdJ-D3X_vtk2tiXNgWtXzARTHIYoAwNMYfUPrZE9-_4c_JgVtg6AqnDfGobXEOzV4HMxQI21BPA1JxxsoayMteV88ZyNFJ_K5ZjYuBmA0-1BkC8KF9cjcvcwuRCmcqPeaLJMsMJyuyn1lcMaBbN2fu78391lhMGFy807e-oXYtcvhisaD3OFojjAPZGn-zwrOFLmbBqQzPwJOUgvdkbhHdUPb86vEjq6LHpkL6xEm04d5ckORzUv3w4oEMFVln99yLW8OvUIrGXD0xMHo/4bqJergVUpeDdqQqfOHtZU-gG2GWN8Ek/8" target="_blank"&gt;资金削弱了马萨诸塞州的主要经济引擎的风险&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;该大学&lt;/strong&gt;周一&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/aRnIVJ088VNjaieEHKJ7TvFYB6B2FIxbypmAaibQR9s94hwBc47FgqylZeuG-McEt5oOx9Ol546laMGYKceyQRB_HAB_WCwrgFnuwrUsfTNx992fNSmKylYSuCh7RFxIlEsRgN_9MTthVFfGOny9Tu62ziSacLEx8eIW0puracVDDThO6_Sp8XGMeSOxNxqNEQ0QlK6PTIibrt54rMaSaBNQEZpglJaRUIVeyXmAU5Oe39AMavueH2uLpzOO5ddItMTtPSM27CbLSd4rzF1hVYCjOaD4IrWz9ve4UtoPKbM5S_ask42YSqGubo_T6_dK-bfoAGEkP0Ggu1ZhC18IWhLPnTPdCpSoRx0JQa06Z5-R1jdnUtu8ZXXxr4E/oN1hvhcpG3XHth8N3blPi2F0X15ECc7c/8" target="_blank"&gt;拒绝与特朗普政府达成协议，&lt;/a&gt;因为威胁要削减多达90亿美元的财政支持。但是，报应很快就有&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/IhhNCAPotGwqenzbkObKgdIYQu63MexoFmbMQRjJ9GbjgeL7NvxcfrEyvTE2wk_O4qFljVYshpJGeAgyLo-D1NZGZ4hVLxoVFqMZux2q8UuJp2Ja8srzzJlIihNYFbkfd3-95zbuEKTPWApRnKMkIMwSeOhU4QyZRotKa_EHPPFhUrLIRWQI33m4bJOIZ7j3Ed4Qd_LnZI_dB1jDo05s_8lHiDLb4UQat4jov6ThkRx8Ej_bi8QhJIEWXcXaSfzXz4EgllWvJsUqlp0eSqdkxYs4fiFv0FVjUI33VrZ5rn37t8m8F0DoB0yQh3PbG3AakFmLO6bM3mtTMKsdBsB84GYjqtR2iTYHR_pb7FfG54KMpV9EyvE3MhiBnsE/FT1iqO77CbiZfiY2_JCfAJ4hxVOUM-gC/8" target="_blank"&gt;计划冻结哈佛大学的赠款&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;这种反抗&lt;/strong&gt;可能会付出代价。流经学校的联邦资金与主要的医疗系统有关，产生了吸引公司的人才库。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;根据马萨诸塞州的独立大学和大学协会的数据，&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;该州和大学&lt;/strong&gt;在该州提供32万多个工作岗位，并为当地经济提供710亿美元。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;尽管如此，哈佛大学&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/eQItGFW5YDAAi8BdcELaIdVjzRD2tmijBXbs_2jOK2PkgMRAzadSzCd0NTNHbw_JdAoo6PyEORNSqXOEJ1PzSq_L9hhiXSAJddjKEDRIhwsyDRsRPTvzMN64y_1juN6DudTzJXzMa-K3o6aJsan0F3wfuMi5ZkVpSTnFq93WYlvsaAuYnYvl3Y6DLSeqYN-Qn6ktGcruAXqgTvhB095Xwen3B7XMMOSTN5MD1n-IfiOu9dkt28eff2A7XHE0iQ6ApQaXvTZQUs0YY-qJqtk5LS7TDJRQROH8U5G22MLuZHDj-5eVPVSz-aCXNXuy0Ov12yLE1_yVfXCoKV2Y0Zh75YjIcEwZVXLlM9XS67to32SJszUgT0I6np3R4oc/nmnVE_kAJrednLCtywDobvtmaFEEx0qT/8" target="_blank"&gt;比其他人拥有更多的财务能力&lt;/a&gt;，可以度过潜在的法律和政治斗争。但是资金冻结仍然会产生严重的后果， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/dugN_CYVD6pYtphWFokElSJaOItttBHnDAVItq74KItcDupkcgTEM7kkcVV4pPu_DFEVrsuC60bjaqs-